ource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For uneven bars event finals, each gymnast performs a routine, and the difficulty and execution scores are combined for the overall score.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"uneven bars event finals\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"each gymnast\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficulty and execution scores\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall score\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The higher the difficulty, the better your chances are to medal.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your chances\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top eight gymnasts' bar scores from qualification compete for a chance at medaling.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The top eight gymnasts' bar scores\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"qualification\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles came in ninth place, so she was the first reserve (alternate).\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"ninth place\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"the first reserve\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The favorites going into today's competition were Nemour, who led in qualifications, Qiyuan who was second in qualifications, and Lee, who came in third in qualifications and earned the bronze in the 2020 Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.999999998960674