tte work\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"her Hindorff\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"one full point\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"deductions\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she gets back up and finishes the routine, her score is a disappointing 12.8 score, which is almost two points lower than her qualifying score.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the routine\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"her score\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"a disappointing 12.8 score\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"her qualifying score\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italy's Alice D'Amato shows stunning lines and dismounts with a double front, scoring a 14.733 and taking an early lead.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9627166414863388, \"rank\": 0.03642420950244459, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice D'Amato\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stunning lines\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"dismounts\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"a double front\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"an early lead\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Belgium's Nina Derwael, the